            <h2>25k Grant for h241</h2>
            <p>
               I remember feeling extremely nervous when we were waiting to hear back about the grant. We had this fantastic idea and already had 100 users in 3 days, but we were stuck with some critical bugs that kept us from having a functional MVP. When they announced the winners for the usual prizes, ranging from $2K to $1K, I figured it was a lost cause for us. Then, out of the blue, they dropped the bomb that ICP was considering a $25K grant for our project because of its execution, approach and the ideas nature. Even though I kept my cool in response, inside, I was absolutely screaming. Even if we didn't continue development of h241 nor receive the grant this is a very fond memory that kickstarted my startup journey.
